# ABIs Directory
#
# Place the compiled StellarNebulaNomad contract ABI JSON here:
#   StellarNebulaNomad.json
#
# Generate it from your Soroban contract with:
#   soroban contract bindings typescript --wasm <path-to-wasm> --output-dir .
#
# Then copy the generated ABI file here:
#   cp StellarNebulaNomad.json ./abis/
